General Budget Debate, Tuesday, 02 June 2020 JOHANNESBURG - The KwaZulu-Natal MEC for Economic Development, Tourism and Environmental Affairs, Nomusa Dube-Ncube, will table the 2020/2021 budget on Tuesday. Earlier, KZN Premier Sihle Zikalala delivered budget policy speech at the Provincial Legislature. The premier outlined the budget allocation of key priorities for his office.